name: v1.3.0
body:
Update Go to 1.8.1 and dependency to Go 1.7.5
Switch custom cancel signals to use Context
Vendor all dependencies for more stable builds
Add 7zip support based on work from @arcane47
Switch ADB to be the default MAME src
Remove Deprecated Flags
Added Mix images for ScreenScraper

body: Some ScreenScraper bug fixes

name: v.1.2.2
body: Fixes to better handle responses from ScreenScraper

name: v1.2.1
body: Add support for more ScreenScraper regions and restrict the number of connections that are opened based on the users quota.

name: v1.2.0
body:
- Deprecated `-use_*` flags in favor of `-console_src` and `-mame_src` that accept ordered lists of sources to try. 
- Added `-max_height` parameter similar to `-max_width`
- Update ScreenScraper API to v2
- Add support to ScreenScraper with MAME
- Change `-strip_unicode`default to `false`
- Add mitigation for 429 errors when downloading hash.csv

name: v1.1.10
body:
Add ScreenScraper.fr as a source use `-use_ss=true -use_gdb=false` to use it. Added options `-region` `-lang` for the new multilingual/regional source. Renamed `-gdb_img` to `-console_img`

`-refresh` and `-append` now remove roms that don't exist and persist lastplayed, playcount, and favorites.

Update to go 1.7.1

name: v1.0.9
